{
  "id": "RAW_680230",
  "title": "Notion 发布三个 AI 新功能，他们终于知道怎么用 AI 了",
  "url": "http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg5NTc0MjgwMw==&mid=2247516197&idx=2&sn=736e9754aa966ead6aaec43cad42cf74",
  "date": "2025-05-14 12:30:00",
  "author": "StartupBoy",
  "siteName": "Founder Park",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 2 []\"><br></section>\n   <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span data-eleid=\"9\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI 笔记产品 Notion 今天发布了 3 个 AI 新功能，分别为&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Al Meeting Notes、Notion AI for Work 和 Research Mode。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span data-eleid=\"9\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">其中，</span></span><span data-eleid=\"9\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;text-only&quot;,&quot;data-eleid&quot;:&quot;9&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Al Meeting Notes 功能，被定位为 Notion 工作流中的「功能」，而不是一个独立的工具产品，目的在于将生成的会议笔记内容巧妙、无感知地融入到用户现有的工作流程中。</span></span></span></span></p><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 1em 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;display: block;font-size: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Notion 创始人 Ivan Zhao 认为，AI 将彻底改变我们未来的工作方式，而&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Notion 正在将自己打造成一个 All-In-One AI 平台。<br></span></span></span></section><section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <hr style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;transform:scale(1, 0.5);border-right-width:0px;letter-spacing:0.578px;border-bottom-width:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);transform-origin:0px 0px;border-style:solid;border-left-width:0px;\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(75, 110, 245);font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-vari