uot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 16px;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 36px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></span></strong></span></section><section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(75, 110, 245);font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 4 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-tool&quot;:&quot;mdnice编辑器&quot;,&quot;data-website&quot;:&quot;https://www.mdnice.com&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 36px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 16px;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 36px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">01&nbsp;</span></span>\n     <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:16px 0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(75, 110, 245);font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.5px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">AI 笔记功能：</span></strong></p>\n     <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:16px 0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(75, 110, 245);font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.5px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">无感知、深度集成</span></strong></p></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一个是增加了</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI 会议笔记，真正将 AI 会议笔记变成了一个功能（feature）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。我简单体验了一下，效果非常不错，可能会给很多其他 AI 会议笔记带来非常重大的挑战，特别是如果你或者你的公司本身已经在使用 Notion 了，那么你可能就不需要再用其他 AI 笔记会议工具了。</span></span></span></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个功能 Notion 做得非常巧妙，几乎没有任何感知，直接在 Notion 任何页面输入/meet 这个命令或者点击 Meet 按钮就可以了，之后它会自动将会议纪要按照 Summary、Notes 和 Transcript 的方式记录下来。</span></span></strong></span></p>\n   <section style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6805216c-210b-4e6b-d1d4-79cb08d80400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6203605514316013\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"943\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"308372769\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6805216c-210b-4e6b-d1d4-79cb08d80400/public\">\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">对于本身就已经在使用 Notion 的人来说，这种方式基本上让你无感，不需要单独打开另一个 AI 会议笔记工具，也没有所谓的 AI 机器人参与线上会议，并且由于会议的内容是在 Notion 页面记录的，你也可以手动记录或者添加自己的的想法。我自己简单体验了一下，确实是非常方便。</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且此次 Notion 还将日历也打通了，不仅可以直接在日历里将所有会议记录存储在 Notion 上的一个单独数据库，这样以后所有的会议就全部在 Notion 的一个数据库里了。</span></span></span></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">同时，Notion 称你还可以将 AI 会议记录添加到任何一个日历活动中，直接在 Notion 日历里选择之前的会议笔记即可，基本上日历、AI 会议和 Notion 的所有功能全部无缝衔接了起来。</span></span></span></p>\n   <section style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d05ae66f-2f3f-492c-8c87-a1d0263e3000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6197033898305084\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"944\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"308372763\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d05ae66f-2f3f-492c-8c87-a1d0263e3000/public\">\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你还可以选择会议的风格以及大概的场景，比方说融资会议和企业销售业务的笔记风格可能就不一样，这样记录的笔记会按照不同场景的方式来记录，相当于提供了一些特定场景的模板，这也是之前很多 AI 会议笔记非常受欢迎的一个功能，比方说创投圈最喜欢的这款 AI 会议笔记产品《</span><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMDA3MjMwNw==&amp;mid=2455855209&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=30bc01fbbee0bdac331d36e0cad96e99&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"又一 AI 笔记拿了 2000 万美金核心针对创投人群，一创投 Newsletter 收入超 200 万美金\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">又一 AI 笔记拿了 2000 万美金核心针对创投人群，一创投 Newsletter 收入超 200 万美金</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">》。</span></span></span></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">另外，由于笔记内容是记录在 Notion 里面的，因此这个页面也可以实时协作的，参与会议的人可以同时在这个页面记录自己的想法和关心的重点，并且@ 某些人关注某些特定会议内容，这就把 AI 自动记笔记和人工记录结合了起来，同时通过实时协作功能让这个产品更加面向的是多人会议，而非一对一这种。</span></span></span></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">之后，还可以通过 Notion AI 帮助你写邮件以及做项目跟进等后续事务。因此整体来看，我觉得 Notion 的 AI 会议笔记功能不再是一个单独的工具，而是和整个 Notion 上的数据、人员以及工作任务全面打通的整套解决方案了。</span></span></span></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Notion 对 AI 会议笔记的整合，让我觉得真正在将 AI 笔记从一个单独的工具产品变成了一个功能（feature），现在基本上所有线上会议工具也都有了类似功能，未来可能各种产品都将具备这个功能。</span></span></span></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就在今天，Perplexity CEO 说他们即将推出的 Agentic 浏览器也将推出 AI 会议笔记功能，提供原生虚拟会议录制、转录和搜索功能。</span></span></strong></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></strong></span></p><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(75, 110, 245);font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decor